本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:葉燕容論文名稱:金庸小說《倚天屠龍記》研究論文名稱(外文):A Study of “Heaven Sword And Dragon Sabre”,a novel of Jin Jong指導教授:陳光憲學位類別:碩士校院名稱:臺北市立教育大學系所名稱:中國語文學系碩士班學門:人文學門學類:中國語文學類畢業學年度:95語文別:中文中文關鍵詞:金庸、武俠小說、倚天屠龍記、寫作藝術外文關鍵詞:Jin Yong、Martial Arts Novels、Heaven Sword And Dragon Sabre、Arts of Writing相關次數:

被引用:24點閱:985評分:下載:0書目收藏:3



《倚天屠龍記》是金庸的長篇力作之一，敘事結構龐大而複雜，出場人物眾多且各具特色，對於人性的複雜與矛盾，發人深省，集文學性、藝術性、傳奇性、趣味性於一體，表現了作者組織情節、運用語言、塑造人物的高度技巧。書中的情節變化無窮，敘述明晰流暢，人物各具特色，這部小說在藝術性的表現上，達到了相當大的水準，不但是武俠小說的佼佼者，也是當代漢語文學的優秀作品。為了使優秀的武俠小說得到公允的評價，因此，本論文以《倚天屠龍記》這部小說作為研究主題。本論文凡五章。第一章〈緒論〉：作為本論文的引述，說明研究動機、研究目的、研究範圍與方法，並將論文架構做一簡單概略的呈現。第二章〈金庸及其小說〉。在本章當中，分成三節。第一節為「金庸生平」，介紹作家的生平事蹟，及表列其創作年表，讓小說家的生命轉折，與時代發展脈絡，有清晰的呈現與對照，以期更貼近金庸的創作世界。第二節為「金庸小說」，包括探析在臺灣、大陸及海外地區金庸小說的現況，金庸小說的版本系統，進而探究金庸小說受歡迎的原因。第三節為「金庸小說研究概況」，含括臺灣、大陸及海外地區金庸小說的研究概況，金庸小說在文學的評價，以及金庸小說引起的爭論。第三章〈《倚天屠龍記》寫作藝術（上）〉。本章共分成三節，就《倚天屠龍記》的「主題思想」、「情節架構」、「敘事模式」等方面進行探討，研究其形式方面的寫作藝術。第四章〈《倚天屠龍記》寫作藝術（下）〉。本章共分成三節，就《倚天屠龍記》的「人物刻畫」、「環境描寫」、「語言運用」等方面進行探討，研究其內容方面的寫作藝術。第五章〈結論〉。據本論文第二、三、四章對《倚天屠龍記》進行各層面的剖析，本章提出總結論述，並嘗試說明在中國大陸出生、香港崛起的金庸，其作品風靡華人世界，其小說中對人生的啟發意義，引人深思，小說不僅是知識寶庫，更能淨化人心，肯定金庸的小說在中國文學史上的價值與意義。

A Study of “Heaven Sword And Dragon Sabre”, a novel of Jin Yong“Heaven Sword And Dragon Sabre”, one of the greatest full-length novels from Jin Yong, composes a big and complicated descriptive structure and arranges numerous and variable characters and stimulates deep thoughts by descriptions of complexity and conflicts of human beings. It is literature full of arts, legends and interests and manifests writer’s great skills in structuring plots, using languages and forming characters as well. We have seen variable turns in plots, simple but smooth descriptions and distinguishing characters in this novel, and those features make it achieve high standard of arts. It is not only a great work in the martial arts novel, but also in contemporary Chinese literature. To make this excellent martial arts novel have fair judgments, the thesis takes “Heaven Sword And Dragon Sabre” as the subject of study.The thesis has five chapters. Chapter one, “Preface”, introduces the thesis, explains motivation, goal, range and method of study, and generally presents the structure of the thesis.Chapter two, “Jin Yong And His Works”, has three sections. Section one, Introduction of Jin Yong, describes writer’s life, chronicles his works in order to manifest clear presentation and comparison of novelist’s changes in life with development of the times and step further into Jin Yong’s world of creation. Section two, Jin Yong’s novels, observes the fad to Jin Yong’s novels in Taiwan, Mainland China and overseas, lists different versions of Jin Yong’s novels in order to find out the reasons, which makes Jin Yong’s novels popular. Section three, General description of studies of Jin Yong’s novels, introduce studies in Taiwan, Mainland China and overseas and judgments in literature and disputes aroused by Jin Yong’s novels.Chapter three, Arts of writing of “Heaven Sword And Dragon Sabre” 1, has three sections and discusses the novel in terms of thoughts of subject, structure of plots and mode of description. Chapter four, Arts of writing of “Heaven Sword And Dragon Sabre 2”, uses three sections to analyze the form of novel. It discusses the novel in terms of depiction of characters, descriptions of environment and usage of language.Chapter five, Conclusion, presents conclusive arguments, tries to explain the fad and inspirations of works by Jin Yong, who born in Mainland China and became famous in Hong Kong, and confirms these works’ status and importance in the history of Chinese Literature.

